FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."PasswordHash", u."Username"
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE u."Username" = @__request_Username_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."UserId", u0."RoleId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRoles" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Roles" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS s ON u1."Id" = s."UserId"
ORDER BY u1."Id", s."UserId", s."RoleId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."PasswordHash", u."Username"
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE u."Username" = @__request_Username_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."UserId", u0."RoleId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRoles" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Roles" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS s ON u1."Id" = s."UserId"

    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."Email", u."PasswordHash", u."Username"
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE u."Username" = @__request_Username_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."UserId", u0."RoleId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRoles" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Roles" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS s ON u1."Id" = s."UserId"
